Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.70,0:00:05.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.53,0:00:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小涼宮春日的憂鬱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.29,0:00:14.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.86,0:00:16.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.60,0:00:21.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換衣凳上出現了好多我沒見過的衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.82,0:00:24.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  大概是長門的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.50,0:00:26.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近她收集了很多的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.91,0:00:29.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.02,0:00:30.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.31,0:00:33.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為Cosplay角色而產生了競爭情緒！？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.55,0:00:36.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虛  請用茶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.93,0:00:38.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…啊  非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:41.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虛  請用茶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.48,0:00:42.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.06,0:00:45.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虛  請用茶！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.45,0:00:46.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罰酒三杯！？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.94,0:00:48.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  阿虛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.44,0:00:50.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在舉行化裝舞會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.92,0:00:51.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.36,0:00:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虛…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.09,0:00:54.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.64,0:00:55.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.55,0:00:57.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦！朝比奈學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:03.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就憑我也去挑戰長門同學根本就是個錯誤…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.28,0:01:05.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能笑  不能笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.34,0:01:08.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.44,0:01:10.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服非常適合朝比奈學姐你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.42,0:01:12.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請拿出自信來…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.92,0:01:13.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.92,0:01:15.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（其實是隻熊哦）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.28,0:01:24.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  長門啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.28,0:01:24.90,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（這語調是在模仿谷口嗎…）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.30,0:01:25.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.41,0:01:28.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  已經通關啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.61,0:01:30.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很感人的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.34,0:01:31.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.79,0:01:37.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我借你遊戲  漫畫和輕小說版
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.18,0:01:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.97,0:01:42.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…借給我是很開心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.21,0:01:45.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一下子借這麼多可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.71,0:01:46.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.94,0:01:48.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些是借閱用
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.41,0:01:51.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道還有傳說中的保存用  觀賞用  布教用的嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.41,0:01:51.89,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（宅方淚目…）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.37,0:01:54.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便  我還有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.89,0:01:55.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,續篇！？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.95,0:01:58.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經決定要動畫化了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.79,0:01:59.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…真是耀眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:02.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  阿虛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.57,0:02:04.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來挺重的呢  我幫你拿一半吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.10,0:02:06.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不…這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.19,0:02:07.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Maid Royal：長門熱衷的感人遊戲）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.60,0:02:09.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虛居然萌女僕～～！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.81,0:02:11.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這是向長門借的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.65,0:02:13.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不贊成阿虛你看色色的東西～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.68,0:02:15.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～不…這是全年齡向的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.74,0:02:31.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我依稀地感覺到…上面我夠不著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.74,0:02:31.56,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（呃…朝倉同學您怎麼變成夕映腔了…）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.94,0:02:34.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有個大小合適的台座就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.10,0:02:37.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對…就是這樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.69,0:02:40.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是嬰兒步行器！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.54,0:02:40.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.30,0:02:45.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  每次都要長門同學抱著多麻煩啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.65,0:02:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是得想個法子出來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.34,0:02:51.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的有個大小合適的台座就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.30,0:02:54.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對…就是這樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.54,0:02:56.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別放我坐上去啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.91,0:02:56.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.02,0:02:59.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚…就這樣好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.52,0:03:01.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道這樣很方便啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.19,0:03:03.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣的話也能動就是了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.26,0:03:04.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.19,0:03:05.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:07.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳夠不著啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.93,0:03:10.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那邊的  不要笑啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.60,0:03:13.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了  我再也不認識長門同學了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:17.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:18.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩旋轉木馬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:19.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼想出來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:23.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  這種情況根本不值得高興吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:28.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然…感覺心情是好了一點點了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.58,0:03:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉的速度是挺快的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.75,0:03:32.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還是完全高興不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（和好了）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.31,0:03:38.19,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你是女僕長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.57,0:03:39.54,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.87,0:03:41.22,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  你為什麼會來這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:44.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是主人的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.27,0:03:45.98,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去救那孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.36,0:03:47.73,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:42.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肚子餓了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.84,0:03:46.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來做點什麼吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.34,0:03:51.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…又把我裝在某種嬰兒用品裡了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.95,0:03:56.51,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女僕長  求你不要靠近了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.76,0:03:58.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不是這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.68,0:04:01.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然感覺這麼被裝著挺方便的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.43,0:04:02.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還是放我出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.04,0:04:06.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西你到底是從哪裡買的！叫什麼名字！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.66,0:04:09.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是嬰兒袋的一種吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.33,0:04:09.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.02,0:04:16.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了  我再也不給長門同學做吃的了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.60,0:04:20.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…突然站起來要做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:24.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就唱起歌來啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.51,0:04:28.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…想用唱歌來蒙混過關嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.64,0:04:36.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  現在的我完全沒有心情聽這種輕快的音樂…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.02,0:04:40.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一首要輪到我來唱哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:42.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh～yeah～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.22,0:04:42.70,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（外星人的夜晚是漫長的）
